column5: I have no clue and and me and the mrs are headed up to an outpost cabin ( only cottage on the whole lake)  past n. bay up by the Quebec border for the last week of trout season .    I was wondering if any one would care to share some go to presentations for this time of year?    It's not a huge lake about 2 miles long by two miles wide.  I have been up in the winter with ok success but never in the fall.
I'm 99% sure i know where you're going, and I live just down the road from there.  PM me.
